column1: In view of the foregoing reasons, it is apparent that the learned High Court Judge is
correct in affirming  the Order of the learned Magistrate dated 11.08.2015 and  in
dismissing the application for revision made by the Appellant.

H
ence, we see no reason for us to interfere with the Order of the learned Magistrate
dated 11.08.2015 and the order of the learned High Court Judge dated 14.11.2018.

T
hus, we dismiss this appeal with costs fixed at Rs. 35,000/-.
JUDGE OF THE COURT OF APPEAL
JUDGE OF THE COURT OF APPEAL
